   <category name='moves'>

      <section name='keepout'>

         <para number='1' comment='Turn back non-staff - loc 901'>
         A union representative hurries up to you and tells you this is an active contruction site. "Sorry, sorry," he chants, "No visitors today. Come back tomorrow. Or better still, next week."
         </para>

      </section>

      <section name='noexit'>

         <para number='1' comment='shuttle area'>
         A burly droid glides over and places a heavy hand on your shoulder. "Nah then, nah then, citizen; you can't be wandering off the pathways without authorization."
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='control shed'>
         You stumble against an unyielding glazsteel panel.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='ops shed'>
         Your effort only succeeds in rearranging the rock dust on the floor into an increasingly unsightly mess.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='custers pub'>
         You clumsily stumble into the stacked crates bruising yourself.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='custers pub main'>
         You stumble into a cluster of workers who laugh, spin you around, and push you away.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='rock corridors'>
         You stumble into a rock wall and loudly muttering, you turn away. A miner glares at you.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='sneeze'>
         Your foot slips on the rock dust. Stumbling and stirring up a cloud of rock dust, you sneeze mightily and turn back.
         </para>

         <para number='8' comment='fountain'>
         You attempt to climb up the slippery side of the fountain but your wet hands can find no purchase on the smooth marble. You look for a way to get out.
         </para>

      </section>

   </category>

   <category name='newbod'>

      <section name='message'>

         <para number='1' comment='newbod puzzle [1]'>
         As you enter the bar you are accosted by a dubious-looking character wearing a black leather trench coat. His accent is excruciatingly false - he's obviously been watching too many Lattice spy sit-coms. "We haff vot you are looking for." He beckons you over into a dark corner and opens his trench coat.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='newbod puzzle [2]'>
         You gasp in amazement. Hung in the coat from strategically placed straps are dozens of unmarked illegal bulbs of coffee!
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='newbod puzzle [3]'>
         The man smiles a sinister smile and hands you one of the bulbs. "Make zure you teeell all of your friendzz about it. Else..." He draws a finger across his throat. "Zzzzzztt!"
         </para>

      </section>

